  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "In the platformer Drill Dozer, you can take the roll of Jill, the daughter of a crime boss who is set on revenge. When a rival gang steals away her family's heirloom, Jill gives chase in her Drill Dozer, an upgradeable piece of power armor equipped with a large drill. This piece of equipment will help you navigate through six different areas, where you will encounter varied enemies and bosses.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
    },
    {
      "text": "Doug -- who is the leader of a bandit gang known as The Red Dozers and also Jill's Father -- was ambushed by a rival gang known as the Skullkers. They attacked the Red Dozers to steal the powerful Red Diamond, a gift from Jill's dead mother. To retrieve it, Jill mounts the powerful vehicle, the Drill Dozer!!",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb_storyline"
    },
